"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"KYVE 可以启用数据帮助，制定标准验证以及创建数据流制定标准验证和永久性存储数据流。在 Arweave 的加持下，该方案可以确保可扩展性、不可更改以及这些资源的可用性。\\n\\n借助Moonbeam智能合约，KYVE可兼容EVM。KYVE得到了诸多知名VC的支持，包括Hypersphere Ventures, Coinbase Ventures, Mechanism Capital, CMS Holdings，以及大量知名区块链网络的支持，如Arweave, Avalanche, Solana, Interchain和NEAR。\\n\\n官网：<https://app.kyve.network/>\\n\\n推特：<https://twitter.com/KYVENetwork>\\n\\n### 测试教程\\n\\n首先切换到 Moonbase Alpha 网络\\n\\n大家可以到[chainlist](https://chainlist.org/)去添加Moonbase测试网络。\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F0dUzqTOoPN54WNfScO_p2.png&w=1080&q=90)\\n\\n### 领取测试代币\\n\\n登陆[KYVE](https://app.kyve.network/)网站点击水龙头。\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F1dLFULJhRsMwzGNrFE4Kk.png&w=1920&q=90)\\n\\n### 参加资助\\n\\n返回首页选择Aurora，选择Funders点击进入Manage funds。\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2Fz7biIPQ4uTFAYcGcJBWyT.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n输入你资助的数量，注意饮食最低资助金额是你最低资助金额。\\n\\n### 节点委托\\n\\n选择Nodes，点击Manage delegate of nodes I delegated in。\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2F8PKYLCpmiksaTRJUb7oPg.jpg&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n搜索节点地址：0x66317DE4Ab57d6Ecc1623269251101D2934EaF74，填写委托数量即可。\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FD0eNiF2XQ8mwU5IL3Mak5.jpg&w=1920&q=90)\\n\\n转自：\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/0xc522C7497Be47aDc9177Cf536dd84567B7343E62/DC57-Ri4pZn2eHd8EWOkn52bnfJ3mUfxuUODZlX4p3Y](https://mirror.xyz/0xc522C7497Be47aDc9177Cf536dd84567B7343E62/DC57-Ri4pZn2eHd8EWOkn52bnfJ3mUfxuUODZlX4p3Y)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1639973209,\"title\":\"月河链 KYVE测试网交互教程 — Mirror--RW\"},\"digest\":\"3as0ln1-82429YR5QeamV0sANZhqgqKFzmqo39bQsf8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0BC2f9A34c0dadB8604a264b012358F02dedB68F\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"T7Fg_ux461ebj8KOFns8iJ9weAqGFTfaBLpeOk4cS18\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"US0u3XnIPVETE6v95mCoctnp2ijqQ7d8e9GylTliqVU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"w3AJ1Gt1K6HTRPQwxeO1a_qsxGReXXADYSCQAPawxxPQ1P0Ql5rWhBDEPUo8pFUSBQ8MHNpaibPTU4Xx8EJZVQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x520aa28d20f2aa78f24781ec3265aef814f6f89ef6c70d83a14549e84702baa3425894368a72a6629674af9e00d27d5dbda568b04e60f9f027f1e1695b3ad4551c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"T7Fg_ux461ebj8KOFns8iJ9weAqGFTfaBLpeOk4cS18\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"US0u3XnIPVETE6v95mCoctnp2ijqQ7d8e9GylTliqVU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"3as0ln1-82429YR5QeamV0sANZhqgqKFzmqo39bQsf8\"}"